{"id": 1988, "genre": 1001, "title": "相比和事佬型宽容，你觉得理性的宽容是什么样？", "description": "“来都来了”“想想孩子”“给个面子”“都不容易”“差不多得了”……还是整点有用的吧。（题图来自：pixabay）", "record_count": 1993, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171102145220Nh9WgxMkfaFdmGqP.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-03T03:00:29Z", "options": [{"id": 246273, "content": "沉默", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786373}, {"id": 246275, "content": "先把自己给宽容了吧，毕竟要是连自己都不能宽容自己，又谈何宽容别人呢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144137}, {"id": 246276, "content": "哦哦哦哦哦小", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174801}, {"id": 246278, "content": "我不认同你，但我接受你的存在", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1071248}, {"id": 246279, "content": "心软", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1084988}, {"id": 246280, "content": "我维护你涨价的权利，但是也请你必须承担相应的责任和义务。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173724}, {"id": 246281, "content": "当对方认识到问题时，才宽容。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174844}, {"id": 246282, "content": "对事不对人", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814778}, {"id": 246283, "content": "来看看", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174850}, {"id": 249355, "content": "\n不会对正确的但是和自己相反的观点恶语相向", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1179559}, {"id": 246285, "content": "理性的成全", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174850}, {"id": 246286, "content": "不道德绑架也不无限放大一件小事；不轻易原谅别人，也不轻易憎恨谁。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174533}, {"id": 246289, "content": "理性的宽容就是有节制地凶恶", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155587}, {"id": 246545, "content": "在合乎法理和原则的基础上，即便不认同或是不支持，但也给予充分尊重和选择权。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945317}, {"id": 246290, "content": "1.理性 2. 宽容", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723879}, {"id": 247826, "content": "吃软不吃硬", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1177376}, {"id": 246291, "content": "讲道理，输了我认", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174360}, {"id": 246292, "content": "事情起因的真实回复", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173977}, {"id": 246548, "content": "所谓的理性宽容无非是建立在利益的等价性和可交换性上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173378}, {"id": 246293, "content": "根据实际情况断定，该宽和时会做和事佬，但在处理原则性问题时，该严肃处理就不会浑水摸鱼", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174875}, {"id": 246294, "content": "跟特爱逞嘴上功夫的人不计较", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066613}, {"id": 246295, "content": "理有礼，谅有量", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146198}, {"id": 246551, "content": "三观要正", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1152578}, {"id": 246299, "content": "有自己的原则，也尊重别人的原则", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1164496}, {"id": 246300, "content": "是非分明", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066152}, {"id": 246556, "content": "在不得不发泄的抱怨前停顿三分钟、看是不是还想表达", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923165}, {"id": 246302, "content": "理解可以，但要给出合理的理由。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671399}, {"id": 246558, "content": "嘴上积德，日行一善", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176483}, {"id": 246559, "content": "只要不是原则性的问题都可以原谅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176502}, {"id": 246304, "content": "客观", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173961}, {"id": 247072, "content": "不为没有实质性损失的小事浪费过多精力和时间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201097}, {"id": 246305, "content": "不要想和SB讲道理，不要去理他就是了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154318}, {"id": 246561, "content": "以直报怨", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176498}, {"id": 246306, "content": "对事不对人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737751}, {"id": 246308, "content": "在不违背事情原则的前提下，去理解别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026833}, {"id": 246565, "content": "我可以理解你也可以原谅你，但是这个理要说清楚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 420345}, {"id": 246310, "content": "每个人所在的角度和高度都不一样\n。理解他，但不姑息", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174189}, {"id": 246311, "content": "可以理解和宽容对方，但是自己认为不对的或者希望对方让步的地方也要好好说出来，好好交流而不是争吵", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 195734}, {"id": 246312, "content": "坦诚提出意见，也接受合理批评。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174922}, {"id": 246568, "content": "严于律己，宽以待人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942131}, {"id": 246313, "content": "我曾经在东京买了一件东西，但它把东西寄错地方了，经过和客服对话才知道这是他们的规定（上门提货方式会寄到便民服务点）；但这个规定明显不合理（我在城里他他们却寄到农村的提货点。。。），于是我就和JD客服详细的讲了这事……一个月后JD便制定相应的规定彻底解决的这个问题。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1170451}, {"id": 246314, "content": "来都来了，那就说点啥吧，我们来说说啥是理性宽容吧，我觉得吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146408}, {"id": 246315, "content": "换位思考 将心比心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1060839}, {"id": 246571, "content": "前提是对方认识到自己的错误 然后我也认识到自己错误", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176706}, {"id": 246317, "content": "大概是对一些颤颤巍巍反应能力跟不上这个时代的年轻人的老人的温声吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1171842}, {"id": 246318, "content": "世界因不同而美好，我不想去以i自己的标准要求别人，也期盼着别人不要以他们的要标准要求我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772313}, {"id": 246320, "content": "对于理性宽容，我认为那是一种超越了情感控制的，权衡利弊下的宽容，或许有时会很无奈", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 963716}, {"id": 246576, "content": "我能理解你，但不代表我认同你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796354}, {"id": 246321, "content": "允许别人不开心\n而不是总是无知的问：你怎么不开心\n给低落的人留点尊严", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174944}, {"id": 246322, "content": "无需假装", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810467}]}